profile:
Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
INSTANT FREE QUOTE
WE DO NOT HIDE ~ OUR PRICING IS AVAILABLE ONLINE

Click on the Links Above for Pricing Details on POSTS, DECKS and FENCES



What We Do
Perfect Post Hole & Fence is the source for all of your fencing needs. In business and serving the Greater Toronto Area since 1987, we specialize in augured post holes. We drill and set post holes for the D-I-Y homeowner, making their job that much easier. We will also build your fence for you completely, leaving you free to enjoy a beautiful finished product without the work. Our staff members are licensed carpenters and our business is Metro licensed and insured. Call one of our multiple locations to schedule an appointment today! Perfect Post Hole & Fence makes fence building fun!

Fence design and installation

Designs to fit any landscape. Choose from cedar, pressure treated, vinyl, chain link, or wrought iron. Let us know your preferred design or rely on us to make your dream fence become a reality.



Deck design and installation

Choose your design, choose your finish or let us design it for you!



Machine Augered Posthole Digging

Our brand new compact landscape John Deere tractor with turf tires will not damage your lawn. Holes can be dug 9" or 12" in diameter and up to 4 feet deep.



Setting of Posts

Perfect Post and Fence have developed a method of post setting that virtually eliminates frost heave. We set the concrete deep to ensure strength and rigidity for your fence and deck posts. We have the equipment and expertise for all types of post setting.

Proweld is your choice for Wrought Iron Railings, Stainless Steel Railings, Glass Railings, Aluminum Railings, Gate, Fence,Indoor,Outdoor.

Pro Weld provides complete welding services, fabrication and mobile welding services. Pro Weld has been serving the Greater Toronto Area communities for over 20 years. We are CWB certified.

The company was established in 1990, with customer service and professionalism in mind.

We provide complete mobile welding and fabrication services. We are equipped to handle large and small, residential and industrial projects.

We are experienced with all types of general welding and specialty welding:

    Certified High Pressure Welders
    Heavy Equipment Repairs
    On site Fabrication
    Welding on Steel, Aluminum, Stainless Steel, Cast Iron and all other metals.

Our company specializes in on-site welding of vehicles, modern, commercial, agricultural, classic and prototype. For larger projects we are pleased to offer workshop facilities using the most modern equipment in a fully insured secure environment.

In addition, we provide an onsite welding service to the Construction, Aero and Marine Industries.

We utilize the full range of welding and Plasma cutting equipment including Mig, Tig and Arc, thereby enabling us to weld or cut a range of materials from Mild Steel and Stainless to Cast and Aluminum.

Here is a sample of completed projects that show a range of welding and fabrication assignments. Please fill out a quotation request form or email us, for a free estimate for your specific requirements. Pro Weld has the experience and expertise to do the job right! Your satisfaction is our number one concern, and we would be happy to handle any welding project from start to finish. Call us to get your project on the right track.

Sincerely,
Tal Drori – President
Pro Weld Ltd.

GTA Grizzly is a relatively young company with fresh and modern look at the work process!
⠀
GTA Grizzly is here to help you!
⠀
We strive not only to fulfill your needs, but to solve your problems in a fast, aesthetic and professional manner!
⠀
We are a young player on the market and it is incredibly important to go above and beyond your expectations. We work on our reputation, we want you to spread the word about us and we always strive to implement all your ideas.
⠀
Why are we unique? We have implemented a new way to estimate the costs with high level of accuracy! Forget about unexpected or hidden charges! Forget about quotes “from the top of my mind”, that is normal for most of the companies. We have made this step forward in savings and comfort! GTA Grizzly takes care about the client, because you don’t have to adjust your schedule for extra meetings with us.
⠀
Our team consists of experienced professionals with “burning” eyes for the work. Every client is special and we approach every contract with high level of responsibility, because our reputation is #1 goal for the company. There will be no deficiencies in our work and we are ready to improve the service until we see the smile on your face.
⠀
GTA Grizzly - quality is our power!

We service Commercial and Residential properties all around the GTA.

- Decks and Fences
- Railings
- Powerwashing 
- Parking Lot Maintenance
- Hardscaping and Interlock 
- Flagstone
- Concrete and Stone Steps
- Snowremoval

profile:
After 15 years in the construction industry, we know what Canadian contractors want; great prices without compromising on quality or style -- all made to withstand Canadian weather.
 
We made it happen. Ecowood Composite Materials Inc. is a Canadian brand, based in Toronto Ontario, that offers a new option to contractors and homeowners looking for new ways to beautify their homes. 

Deforestation in Canada is among the world’s lowest, making our country a world leader in sustainable forest management. Canadian forests are healthy, productive and thriving. Ecowood Composite Inc. is dedicated to helping this initiative by providing high quality alternative products to lumber.

All of our products go through a rigorous R&D process and testing and include a limited lifetime warranty.

profile:
Why Trust Us?
From the day we got into business, our goal has been to work on every house as if it were our own. By combining the finest craftsmanship with a level of attention to detail you won’t find anywhere else in the Toronto Area, we’ve made it possible for anyone to create their dream backyard with nothing more than a quick call to the experts they can trust.

Life and Nature...
Everything we do is built from our love of nature and the great outdoors which we get from our founders. They fell in love with woodwork and construction, and decided to create a business that allowed them to share their passion with people right across the local area. At that moment Yardcore Landscaping Design was born and we haven’t looked back since.

By working side by side with every customer and client, we can offer the expert input and finishing touches you won’t find anywhere else. For us it’s not about finishing the job as quickly as possible and moving on to the next property. It’s about creating something that’s built to last that the owners can enjoy for years to come. That way when you hire our team to create the backyard you’ve always wanted, you can sleep with the peace of mind that only comes from knowing you’ve partnered with a team that cares as much about the end result as you do.



Stand on Quality...
We take pride in what we do, and go to great lengths to ensure every fence we erect and deck we lay fits seamlessly into its surroundings. It’s an approach that allows you to reconnect with nature, celebrate everything it has to offer, and enjoy your new space like never before. Not only that, but we also truly believe in what we do. That’s why we offer an exclusive 5 year workmanship warranty with everything we put our name to.

Whether you’re putting the finishing touches to a brand new property, or treating a much loved property to something new, we’re always ready and waiting to lend a hand. It means when you want quality craftsmanship, expert after service, and a team that will always get the job done right the first time, all you have to do is ask.

Life is just better that way.

profile:
MTM General Contracting has been servicing Toronto for over 10 years. We are family owned contracting company with employees that achieved over 10-15 years of experience in renovations. MTM specializes in interior and exterior renovations and re-modelling. The services we offer for interior are kitchen renovations, bathroom renovations, painting, tiling, and flooring. The services we offer for exterior include interlocking, decks, fences, patios, gazebos, car ports, driveway re-levelling, retaining walls, flower beds, and stone work.

MTM General Contracting has provided services to hundreds of clients with the GTA that have had a difficult time finding the perfect contractor to satisfy their needs. We have helped clients turn their small, tight spaced homes into open concept designs with a moderate amount of living space. Clients who spend most of their time in the kitchen have loved the idea of re-modelling their cabinets with as much storage as possible. We have transformed backyards from a small patio into an outstanding patio with beautiful interlocking and firepits for those beautiful summer nights. Here at MTM General Contracting we provide top quality service. Dream. Plan. Build. is the motto and we live by our words. Our employees go above and beyond to keeping clients satisfied with the design and quality of our workmanship.

We assist our clients beforehand with 3D rendering and drawings. We provide our clients with their dream home design and show the final layouts of the project before starting the work. We work with top quality softwares that provide us with tools and products which can show selections down to the details. Our mission is to always keep our clients satisfied with the work we provide. MTM General Contracting treats their client’s homes just as if it’s their own. Unlike other contractors, we are always there to answer questions and give suggestions when needed even afterhours. We strive to make sure our clients have open communication with MTM General Contracting at all times to make sure whatever changes that need to done are honoured. 

Your dream brought to reality!

Our service locations are anywhere in Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Oakville, Scarborough, North York, Markham, Richmond Hill, Ajax and Pickering.

For additional information, feel free to contact us at any time for a free quote.

Mohammad Mansouri

Phone:  (647) 240-4536

profile:
We have been in the post hole digging industry for over 15 years. The Post Hole Diggers prides itself on its integrity, dependability and high quality workmanship. We value our customers satisfaction above all else and strive to deliver on what we promise. Our staff is professional, well trained, and eager to help and strongly believe that no job is too big, too small, or too hard as they always say If there is a will there is a way!!


We have managed over our 15 years in the business to build a reputation for our quality work and our professionalism which has given rise to large contracts with many contractors, construction companies and land developers. We are proud to say that our work speaks for itself and we get many happy repeat customers and referrals for it. We know you will be satisfied with us. Feel free to browse our testimonials for some feedback and reviews.


When working with us, you, the client, can be at ease knowing that we are fully insured for all aspects of the work (from liability to WSIB) and you bear no responsibility should something go wrong. However, we are proud to say that in 15 years we have never had to make any claims for any work related accidents. We always make sure to take all the necessary safety precautions to ensure a safe work environment for our clients and for our employees.
